---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="About | Offsite Social Co." description="The story behind the club." />
		<style>
			:root {
				--bg-color: #0d2821; 
				--text-main: #f5e6d3; 
				--text-muted: #d9cbb8;
				--accent: #e08b6c; 
				
				/* The Industrial Academic Font Stack */
				--font-academic: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
				--font-industrial: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
				--font-ui: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
			}
			body {
				background-color: var(--bg-color);
				color: var(--text-muted);
				font-family: var(--font-academic);
				font-size: 1.15rem;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				line-height: 1.75;
				-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
			}
			h1 {
				font-weight: normal;
				color: var(--text-main);
				margin-top: 0;
				font-size: 3rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245, 230, 211, 0.2);
				padding-bottom: 1rem;
				margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
			}
			.container {
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 6rem 2rem;
			}
			.header-nav {
				margin-bottom: 4rem;
			}
			.header-nav a {
				color: var(--text-main);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-family: var(--font-industrial);
				text-transform: uppercase;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				letter-spacing: 1.5px;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
				padding-bottom: 4px;
				transition: all 0.2s ease;
			}
			.header-nav a:hover {
				color: var(--accent);
			}
			.tag {
				background-color: rgba(224, 139, 108, 0.1);
				color: var(--accent);
				padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				font-family: var(--font-industrial);
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 2px;
				border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				display: inline-block;
			}
			p {
				margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
				max-width: 65ch;
			}
			.sign-off {
				margin-top: 4rem;
				padding-top: 2rem;
				border-top: 1px dashed rgba(245, 230, 211, 0.2);
				font-family: var(--font-industrial);
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: rgba(245, 230, 211, 0.5);
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 1px;
				line-height: 1.8;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main class="container">
			<nav class="header-nav">
				<a href="/">← Back to the Block</a>
			</nav>

			<span class="tag">The Story</span>
			<h1>About the Project</h1>
			
			<p>Offsite Social Co. was built on a simple observation: the shift to remote work gave us our time back, but it stripped away the passive routines that actually tie a neighborhood together.</p>
			
			<p>Working from home shouldn't mean working in isolation. We don't need more digital groups or forced networking events with name tags. We need a reason to clock out, grab a seat at a familiar table, and be a regular.</p>
			
			<p>This social club acts as a bridge. By partnering with distinct local spots that care about their craft, we create unhurried windows of time for neighbors to cross paths.</p>

			<div class="sign-off">
				Operated by Community Craft, Ltd.<br>
				An independent effort built block by block.
			</div>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>